Who's house is this?

1264
02:15:55.083 --> 02:15:57.167 line:82%
You know Kamaljit,
it's her birthday today.

1265
02:15:57.250 --> 02:15:58.750 line:82%
So I thought I'd invite her for dinner.

1266
02:15:58.833 --> 02:16:00.667 line:82%
If you are with me she will
take me more seriously.

1267
02:16:00.750 --> 02:16:01.583 line:82%
Kamaljit?

1268
02:16:01.708 --> 02:16:05.458 line:82%
Kamaljit. That...

1269
