Dev's mother.

1270
02:16:11.458 --> 02:16:13.333 line:82%
Rhea... Who is it?

1271
02:16:13.542 --> 02:16:17.792 line:82%
Many happy returns of the day.

1272
02:16:24.208 --> 02:16:26.583 line:82%
So how old is Chandigarh?

1273
02:16:26.792 --> 02:16:29.375 line:82%
-Beauty has no age, Sam.
-Really?

1274
02:16:37.417 --> 02:16:39.833 line:82%
The next thing I know,
there'll be nude girls dances.

1275
02:16:39.917 --> 02:16:41.125 line:82%
So you can join them, too.

1276
02:17:19.833 --> 02:17:22.042 line:82%
Our wedding pictures.

1277
02:17:25.500 --> 02:17:27.125 line:82%
You know what I am saying to Dev here?

1278
02:17:27.708 --> 02:17:30.917 line:82%
Now that the vows are made,
I'll kill you if you don't stick to them.

1279
02:17:37.583 --> 02:17:39.000 line:82%
When Arjun was born.

1280
02:17:40.167 --> 02:17:42.375 line:82%
I have never seen Dev so happy.

1281
02:17:45.417 --> 02:17:48.000 line:82%
Rhea, I'm leaving--

1282
02:17:54.375 --> 02:17:57.333 line:82%
OK. Everything is set.
Dinner at my place at 8.

1283
02:17:58.917 --> 02:18:00.135 line:82%
And yes you are invited, too.

1284
02:18:00.208 --> 02:18:02.938 line:82%
But if you're busy
then we shall understand.

1285
02:18:08.083 --> 02:18:10.625 line:82%
You seem to have settled down here.
Should we?

1286
02:18:14.208 --> 02:18:15.667 line:82%
Can I have Dev back please?

1287
02:19:07.292 --> 02:19:08.375 line:82%
I'm getting married.

1288
02:19:11.833 --> 02:19:12.833 line:82%
To Kamal.

1289
02:19:14.125 --> 02:19:14.958 line:82%
What?

1290
02:19:16.292 --> 02:19:19.250 line:82%
That's the expression I wanted to see.

1291
02:19:20.958 --> 02:19:23.042 line:82%
Sam, what are you doing?

1292
02:19:23.167 --> 02:19:24.167 line:82%
Just joking.

1293
02:19:25.833 --> 02:19:28.792 line:82%
You know we have to do something
about your son's sense of humor.

1294
02:19:29.875 --> 02:19:31.583 line:82%
Smile, my son.
Smile.

1295
02:19:32.042 --> 02:19:35.333 line:82%
You won't die if you do. And even if
you die, you will die with a smile.

1296
02:19:49.625 --> 02:19:51.833 line:82%
At last there's someone
who can shut you up.

1297
02:19:51.938 --> 02:19:53.558 line:82%
He is just talking--

1298
02:19:53.708 --> 02:19:58.583 line:82%
Tell me Rishi, was he always like this
or is this change recent?

1299
02:19:58.958 --> 02:20:02.292 line:82%
He behaves like a tiger now,
but he was a mouse before my mother.

1300
02:20:02.375 --> 02:20:03.625 line:82%
Rishi, behave.

1301
02:20:05.250 --> 02:20:07.375 line:82%
His mother was a very strict woman.

1302
02:20:07.542 --> 02:20:11.833 line:82%
She used to say, 'you can look
but don't you dare touch!'

1303
02:20:13.667 --> 02:20:16.958 line:82%
And these days there's no time to look.

1304
02:20:24.958 --> 02:20:27.750 line:82%
It's not about rules, Mr. Talwar.
It's about limits.

1305
02:20:28.625 --> 02:20:30.500 line:82%
It's very easy to slip in a marriage.

1306
02:20:31.125 --> 02:20:33.667 line:82%
It's difficult to keep control.

1307
02:20:34.417 --> 02:20:37.042 line:82%
I personally feel every relationship
should have its boundaries.

1308
02:20:37.583 --> 02:20:40.417 line:82%
And I believe more the boundaries

1309
02:20:40.958 --> 02:20:43.250 line:82%
more the chances of them being crossed.

1310
02:20:47.000 --> 02:20:49.250 line:82%
Maya, you tell me.
What do you think?

1311
02:20:53.542 --> 02:20:58.792 line:82%
Maya doesn't need to draw any boundaries
because her husband loves her too much.

1312
02:21:00.458 --> 02:21:04.417 line:82%
Flattery. Flattery. When a man uses
flattery it only means two things...

1313
02:21:04.500 --> 02:21:07.125 line:82%
Either he is lying
or he is hiding something.

1314
02:21:07.333 --> 02:21:11.458 line:82%
Really. These days Dev is flattering me.

1315
02:21:11.667 --> 02:21:13.042 line:82%
You think I need to worry?

1316
02:21:16.583 --> 02:21:17.417 line:82%
You should.

1317
02:21:20.333 --> 02:21:23.042 line:82%
Everyone's been speaking a lot.

1318
02:21:23.125 --> 02:21:24.375 line:82%
About relationships.

1319
02:21:25.375 --> 02:21:28.458 line:82%
But relationships are not about words
they are about circumstances.

1320
02:21:29.125 --> 02:21:33.000 line:82%
No one knows why one slips
in a relationship.

1321
02:21:34.583 --> 02:21:37.292 line:82%
Why one falls in love
outside a relationship?

1322
02:21:38.792 --> 02:21:40.125 line:82%
No one knows.

1323
02:21:40.667 --> 02:21:44.792 line:82%
Even I don't know why it happened with me.

1324
02:21:48.833 --> 02:21:49.708 line:82%
But it did...

1325
02:21:54.042 --> 02:21:57.438 line:82%
Rhea, I am in love with someone else.

1326
02:22:00.708 --> 02:22:01.542 line:82%
I'm in love.

1327
02:22:04.333 --> 02:22:07.000 line:82%
I'm sorry, Rhea but that's the truth.

1328
02:22:14.708 --> 02:22:19.792 line:82%
And the woman I fell in love with
is right here.

1329
02:22:31.167 --> 02:22:32.375 line:82%
It's Maya.

1330
02:22:54.708 --> 02:22:56.208 line:82%
What happened, Mr. Talwar?

1331
02:23:10.542 --> 02:23:11.917 line:82%
I was going to kill him before you.

1332
02:23:32.958 --> 02:23:34.250 line:82%
What was wrong with you last night?

1333
02:23:34.958 --> 02:23:36.000 line:82%
What were you saying?

1334
02:23:37.167 --> 02:23:38.250 line:82%
You said whatever you felt like.

1335
02:23:38.583 --> 02:23:39.958 line:82%
Did you think of me even once
while saying all those things?

1336
02:23:40.167 --> 02:23:41.750 line:82%
Now who will answer Rishi's questions?

1337
02:23:41.833 --> 02:23:44.458 line:82%
You. Who else? Just tell him the truth.
I don't care.

1338
02:23:44.542 --> 02:23:47.833 line:82%
Tell him the truth? Then what Dev?

1339
02:23:48.208 --> 02:23:49.083 line:82%
Leave the house?

1340
02:23:49.292 --> 02:23:53.667 line:82%
And come to you? Will you leave Rhea
and your son? Tell me.

1341
02:24:46.292 --> 02:24:47.583 line:82%
You were right, Dev.

1342
02:24:50.667 --> 02:24:53.083 line:82%
You never know what you'll get to see
outside this station.

1343
02:25:08.333 --> 02:25:09.167 line:82%
Let's go.

1344
02:25:28.708 --> 02:25:31.000 line:82%
It's all so dirty. Not been cleaned
for so many days.

1345
02:25:31.083 --> 02:25:33.750 line:82%
Will you have coffee?
What will you have, dad?

1346
02:25:33.833 --> 02:25:38.167 line:82%
Coffee? No. This Rishi,
he just keeps anything anywhere.

1347
02:25:38.417 --> 02:25:42.042 line:82%
He's moved everything around.
Dad, you'll have tea?

1348
02:25:42.125 --> 02:25:44.708 line:82%
You never have tea. I'm crazy.

1349
02:25:44.792 --> 02:25:46.917 line:82%
What am I saying?
Just need to clean all this.

1350
02:27:08.042 --> 02:27:08.875 line:82%
You are late?

1351
02:27:10.958 --> 02:27:14.417 line:82%
Yes. Too late.

1352
02:29:14.250 --> 02:29:15.958 line:82%
I wanted to apologize, Dad.

1353
02:29:20.292 --> 02:29:23.417 line:82%
But apologies are for mistakes.

1354
02:29:28.083 --> 02:29:29.750 line:82%
What's the punishment for selfishness?

1355
02:29:32.625 --> 02:29:33.458 line:82%
Tell me, Dad.

1356
02:29:39.125 --> 02:29:40.417 line:82%
I'm a father.

1357
02:29:43.875 --> 02:29:48.125 line:82%
I can't punish.
I can only advise.

1358
02:29:53.208 --> 02:29:54.375 line:82%
Leave Rishi.

1359
02:29:58.292 --> 02:29:59.833 line:82%
You don't love him.

1360
02:30:04.625 --> 02:30:06.208 line:82%
By being with him like this

1361
02:30:06.292 --> 02:30:08.792 line:82%
you are keeping him away from his true

1362
02:30:10.000 --> 02:30:10.958 line:82%
And yourself, too.

1363
02:30:14.917 --> 02:30:20.583 line:82%
These incomplete relationships will
bring happiness to no one.

1364
02:30:27.542 --> 02:30:29.542 line:82%
It's not your fault, Maya.

1365
02:30:35.333 --> 02:30:39.208 line:82%
Love and death

1366
02:30:42.333 --> 02:30:44.542 line:82%
both come uninvited.

1367
02:30:47.417 --> 02:30:48.875 line:82%
No one has any control over them.

1368
02:31:17.167 --> 02:31:19.292 line:82%
He's going away.

1369
02:31:55.375 --> 02:31:56.833 line:82%
Chandigarh...

1370
02:32:21.292 --> 02:32:24.125 line:82%
We knew this was the end of our journey.

1371
02:32:25.000 --> 02:32:28.542 line:82%
These were the last few
breaths of our love story.

1372
02:32:29.417 --> 02:32:30.750 line:82%
We had to collect these moments.

1373
02:32:30.917 --> 02:32:33.833 line:82%
and breathe a new life into
our old relationships.

1374
02:32:35.958 --> 02:32:38.167 line:82%
It was time to go home.

1375
02:32:39.417 --> 02:32:42.792 line:82%
We had to tell Rishi and Rhea the truth.

1376
02:32:44.292 --> 02:32:47.167 line:82%
Because happiness can never bloom
in the shadow of lies.

1377
02:32:48.042 --> 02:32:49.958 line:82%
No one knew this better than us.

1378
02:32:52.458 --> 02:32:53.292 line:82%
Who else?

1379
02:33:52.333 --> 02:33:53.167 line:82%
Rhea...

1380
02:33:59.750 --> 02:34:03.958 line:82%
There's another woman in my life.

1381
02:34:08.250 --> 02:34:09.542 line:82%
I'm not joking.

1382
02:34:13.833 --> 02:34:15.167 line:82%
For the last six months.

1383
02:34:20.167 --> 02:34:25.958 line:82%
But that relationship is over now.

1384
02:34:34.500 --> 02:34:37.958 line:82%
Why it happened.
I don't have any answer.

1385
02:34:45.542 --> 02:34:46.875 line:82%
But now...

1386
02:34:49.875 --> 02:34:55.098 line:82%
I want to give our marriage
another chance.

1387
02:34:58.208 --> 02:34:59.708 line:82%
Do you love her?

1388
02:35:03.375 --> 02:35:04.917 line:82%
How does it matter?

1389
02:35:07.875 --> 02:35:09.125 line:82%
It matters to me.

1390
02:35:16.167 --> 02:35:20.375 line:82%
If I had to do what you did,
would you forgive me?

1391
02:35:27.500 --> 02:35:31.417 line:82%
You wouldn't, Dev.
You would never forgive me.

1392
02:35:49.542 --> 02:35:50.833 line:82%
You will have to leave this house.

1393
02:36:17.542 --> 02:36:20.833 line:82%
Rishi, listen to me.

1394
02:36:21.833 --> 02:36:25.542 line:82%
Listen to me. Rishi. Rishi...

1395
02:37:07.750 --> 02:37:12.583 line:82%
How strange Maya, that you kept
cleaning this house all the time.

1396
02:37:12.667 --> 02:37:15.875 line:82%
and today you have brought
in so much filth.

1397
02:37:16.042 --> 02:37:18.083 line:82%
-Don't say that, Rishi.
-Then what should I say?

1398
02:37:20.458 --> 02:37:21.458 line:82%
What should I do?

1399
02:37:24.208 --> 02:37:25.333 line:82%
Celebrate?

1400
02:37:57.917 --> 02:38:00.042 line:82%
Why did you do this?

1401
02:38:05.208 --> 02:38:07.667 line:82%
I loved you so much.

1402
02:38:10.875 --> 02:38:12.583 line:82%
More than my own self.

1403
02:38:14.042 --> 02:38:15.542 line:82%
More than life.

1404
02:38:18.167 --> 02:38:20.083 line:82%
But it wasn't enough for you, right?

1405
02:38:22.500 --> 02:38:24.958 line:82%
-Right, Maya?
-It's not like that, Rishi.

1406
02:38:25.042 --> 02:38:26.500 line:82%
Then how is it, Maya?

1407
02:38:34.458 --> 02:38:35.292 line:82%
You know...

1408
02:38:38.667 --> 02:38:42.500 line:82%
every morning I woke up
to look into your eyes.

1409
02:38:47.750 --> 02:38:49.542 line:82%
To search for my face.

1410
02:38:57.750 --> 02:38:59.875 line:82%
But now I will only see him.

1411
02:39:04.958 --> 02:39:10.667 line:82%
And I will not be able to bear that.

1412
02:39:14.042 --> 02:39:16.542 line:82%
But that relationship is over, Rishi.

1413
02:39:19.083 --> 02:39:20.875 line:82%
This relationship is over, Maya.

1414
02:39:43.208 --> 02:39:44.667 line:82%
Then I'll leave?

1415
02:39:49.333 --> 02:39:50.667 line:82%
I won't stop you.

1416
02:40:29.875 --> 02:40:30.708 line:82%
Rhea.

1417
02:40:34.000 --> 02:40:35.878 line:82%
I want to say something to you.

1418
02:40:39.698 --> 02:40:42.750 line:82%
Dev didn't ask me before stepping
out of this marriage.

1419
02:40:43.875 --> 02:40:46.708 line:82%
Neither did you ask me
before throwing him out.

1420
02:40:47.667 --> 02:40:53.625 line:82%
But my grandson's eyes ask me
whether I'm going to leave him.

1421
02:40:56.917 --> 02:40:58.542 line:82%
I can't do that, Rhea.

1422
02:41:00.750 --> 02:41:02.792 line:82%
So if you have no objections.

1423
02:41:03.917 --> 02:41:05.708 line:82%
I would like to stay with you.

1424
02:41:08.000 --> 02:41:09.208 line:82%
Can I?

1425
02:42:41.678 --> 02:42:44.833 line:82%
Yeah. Got dialed by mistake.

1426
02:42:46.978 --> 02:42:48.083 line:82%
Are you OK?

1427
02:42:52.917 --> 02:42:56.917 line:82%
Did you... tell Rishi... Rishi?

1428
02:42:57.292 --> 02:43:00.500 line:82%
Yeah I told Rishi everything.

1429
02:43:00.798 --> 02:43:02.125 line:82%
What did he say?

1430
02:43:02.542 --> 02:43:03.958 line:82%
He was very angry at first.

1431
02:43:04.625 --> 02:43:08.918 line:82%
But with time I know he will forgive me.

1432
02:43:17.000 --> 02:43:17.833 line:82%
And Rhea?

1433
02:43:18.958 --> 02:43:22.583 line:82%
Even she will forgive me with time.

1434
02:43:36.538 --> 02:43:37.833 line:82%
Yeah, Rhea, I'm coming.

1435
02:43:39.375 --> 02:43:43.083 line:82%
Even I am at home with Rishi.

1436
02:43:45.458 --> 02:43:46.500 line:82%
Be happy.

1437
02:44:04.875 --> 02:44:05.958 line:82%
Goodbye.

1438
02:44:07.500 --> 02:44:11.458 line:82%
All our relationships were
defined by this one word.

1439
02:44:12.125 --> 02:44:16.417 line:82%
Both of us left our homes
and didn't even tell each other about it.

1440
02:44:17.583 --> 02:44:19.583 line:82%
I had never seen
the hope of meeting again.

1441
02:44:19.667 --> 02:44:24.250 line:82%
Die such a silent death before.

1442
02:45:03.167 --> 02:45:08.500 line:82%
Your heart knows

1443
02:45:09.500 --> 02:45:15.292 line:82%
And so does mine

1444
02:45:16.167 --> 02:45:21.792 line:82%
That our roads

1445
02:45:22.375 --> 02:45:28.125 line:82%
Are meant to part

1446
02:45:28.542 --> 02:45:31.542 line:82%
Far apart

1447
02:45:31.708 --> 02:45:34.750 line:82%
Though we will be

1448
02:45:35.083 --> 02:45:40.667 line:82%
Please don't go away from my memories...

1449
02:45:40.875 --> 02:45:46.583 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1450
