1452
02:46:57.333 --> 02:47:03.333 line:82%
All the mirth in life
have slipped away slowly.

1453
02:47:03.542 --> 02:47:08.750 line:82%
It's the pain that refuses to go away

1454
02:47:09.542 --> 02:47:15.500 line:82%
Tried to wish it away
Tried to laugh it away

1455
02:47:15.833 --> 02:47:21.708 line:82%
But the heart falls to find peace

1456
02:47:22.792 --> 02:47:25.208 line:82%
Falls to find peace

1457
02:47:25.542 --> 02:47:30.792 line:82%
Are these tears? Or is it cinder?

1458
02:47:31.542 --> 02:47:37.083 line:82%
Just fire that flows freely from my eyes

1459
02:47:37.898 --> 02:47:43.398 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1460
02:47:44.218 --> 02:47:49.938 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1461
02:47:50.598 --> 02:47:55.318 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1462
02:48:53.917 --> 02:48:59.750 line:82%
Seasons come and seasons go

1463
02:48:59.833 --> 02:49:05.833 line:82%
But the season of pain is here to stay

1464
02:49:06.375 --> 02:49:12.208 line:82%
The shade of sorrow is so deep

1465
02:49:13.292 --> 02:49:19.083 line:82%
That it will take a while to pale

1466
02:49:19.708 --> 02:49:22.000 line:82%
It won't fade away

1467
02:49:22.375 --> 02:49:28.042 line:82%
Who knows what's to happen ahead

1468
02:49:28.667 --> 02:49:34.417 line:82%
Who knows what's in store for us to bear

1469
02:49:34.558 --> 02:49:38.398 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1470
02:49:41.000 --> 02:49:46.708 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1471
02:49:47.418 --> 02:49:53.318 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1472
02:49:54.208 --> 02:50:00.098 line:82%
Your heart knows

1473
02:50:00.375 --> 02:50:06.333 line:82%
And so does mine

1474
02:50:06.792 --> 02:50:12.750 line:82%
That our roads

1475
02:50:13.000 --> 02:50:18.998 line:82%
Are meant to part

1476
02:50:19.542 --> 02:50:24.917 line:82%
Far apart though we will be

1477
02:50:25.917 --> 02:50:31.833 line:82%
Please don't go away from my memories

1478
02:50:32.258 --> 02:50:37.758 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1479
