Never say goodbye

1481
02:50:51.518 --> 02:50:57.138 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1482
02:50:57.750 --> 02:51:03.625 line:82%
Never say goodbye

1483
02:51:57.917 --> 02:51:58.915 line:82%
Do you know Maya,

1484
02:51:58.999 --> 02:52:01.667 line:82%
that in these three years,
I tried hard to hate you.

1485
02:52:02.875 --> 02:52:07.625 line:82%
To forget you.
But I couldn't.

1486
02:52:10.542 --> 02:52:11.833 line:82%
I couldn't do it, Maya.

1487
02:52:16.375 --> 02:52:21.417 line:82%
You gave up the house,
but the house could never give you up.

1488
02:52:24.292 --> 02:52:27.833 line:82%
You were right. I was a child.

1489
02:52:28.333 --> 02:52:33.583 line:82%
I could never understand you.
And that I realize today.

1490
02:52:38.333 --> 02:52:39.625 line:82%
I have grown up, Maya.

1491
02:52:46.583 --> 02:52:48.167 line:82%
I am in love again.

1492
02:52:50.458 --> 02:52:51.833 line:82%
I'm getting married.

1493
02:52:57.042 --> 02:52:58.250 line:82%
Won't you say anything?

1494
02:53:34.125 --> 02:53:35.875 line:82%
I don't have anyone besides you.

1495
02:54:18.375 --> 02:54:23.208 line:82%
Wherever he is,
he is with us.

1496
02:54:31.167 --> 02:54:32.458 line:82%
He is with you.

1497
02:54:55.658 --> 02:54:57.875 line:82%
I am being a mother
to my son after many years.

1498
02:54:59.042 --> 02:55:04.583 line:82%
At this point I'm happy with this
one relationship and...

1499
02:55:04.792 --> 02:55:06.292 line:82%
You don't have to say anything.

1500
02:55:10.292 --> 02:55:12.542 line:82%
I'll be waiting. OK?

1501
02:55:53.500 --> 02:55:54.458 line:82%
I know.

1502
02:55:56.583 --> 02:55:58.792 line:82%
He probably forgot
that I was leaving today.

1503
02:56:00.417 --> 02:56:01.250 line:82%
Rhea.

1504
02:56:04.625 --> 02:56:07.167 line:82%
I have lost my right
to ask you for forgiveness.

1505
02:56:11.000 --> 02:56:13.338 line:82%
But I don't want to lose
the right to bless you.

1506
02:57:31.875 --> 02:57:36.250 line:82%
Rishi? Your wedding? What about Maya?

1507
02:57:36.583 --> 02:57:39.125 line:82%
Maya and I separated three years ago.

1508
02:57:41.500 --> 02:57:44.875 line:82%
And you here? With Jai?

1509
02:57:45.498 --> 02:57:47.708 line:82%
Dev and I divorced three years ago.

1510
02:57:53.417 --> 02:57:58.333 line:82%
But do Dev and Maya know this?

1511
02:58:30.583 --> 02:58:31.833 line:82%
What's the matter, Maya?

1512
02:58:32.333 --> 02:58:36.417 line:82%
Can't look me in the eye.
Can't face me.

1513
02:58:37.250 --> 02:58:42.375 line:82%
Because you broke my heart? My home?

1514
02:58:45.000 --> 02:58:47.333 line:82%
How could you break something
that was already broken, Maya?

1515
02:58:48.250 --> 02:58:52.917 line:82%
Maybe you shouldn't have filled
the void between Dev and me.

1516
02:58:54.917 --> 02:58:59.417 line:82%
But what could you do?
Dev's love is like that.

1517
02:59:01.098 --> 02:59:04.042 line:82%
Ask me.
I know.

1518
02:59:05.292 --> 02:59:09.375 line:82%
Don't be so large-hearted Rhea
that I feel even smaller.

1519
02:59:09.792 --> 02:59:11.542 line:82%
I'm not that magnanimous.

1520
02:59:12.958 --> 02:59:16.708 line:82%
When Dev told me about you I left him.

1521
02:59:20.458 --> 02:59:22.000 line:82%
But I don't think you know that.

1522
02:59:27.792 --> 02:59:32.792 line:82%
How strange.
The love that changed the destinies

1523
02:59:33.625 --> 02:59:36.250 line:82%
of two homes today stands destitute.

1524
02:59:37.458 --> 02:59:40.917 line:82%
I moved on. Rishi moved on.

1525
02:59:42.478 --> 02:59:44.375 line:82%
The two of you got left behind.

1526
02:59:44.792 --> 02:59:46.417 line:82%
Perhaps that's our punishment.

1527
02:59:46.750 --> 02:59:48.250 line:82%
Such a small punishment?

1528
02:59:49.208 --> 02:59:53.583 line:82%
Try living with Dev.
Then you will know what punishment is.

1529
03:00:06.583 --> 03:00:10.833 line:82%
The girl who gets these flowers
gets a new life.

1530
03:00:12.583 --> 03:00:17.792 line:82%
And new happiness. And I want that girl
to be you, Maya.

1531
03:00:20.625 --> 03:00:22.917 line:82%
Your heart has been searching
for love for many years.

1532
03:00:24.917 --> 03:00:26.500 line:82%
And that love is Dev.

1533
03:00:30.625 --> 03:00:35.750 line:82%
And if you don't hurry now your love
will move further away from you.

1534
03:00:37.000 --> 03:00:38.438 line:82%
Dev is leaving for Toronto.

1535
03:01:43.583 --> 03:01:44.417 line:82%
And Rhea?

1536
03:01:44.792 --> 03:01:48.750 line:82%
Even she will forgive me with time.

1537
03:04:12.500 --> 03:04:14.977 line:82%
Aren't you a little overdressed
for the station?

1538
03:04:20.792 --> 03:04:22.197 line:82%
It's been a while hasn't it?

1539
03:04:23.583 --> 03:04:25.125 line:82%
I don't live here anymore.

1540
03:04:27.042 --> 03:04:28.837 line:82%
And I don't live here despite being here.

1541
03:04:33.625 --> 03:04:37.917 line:82%
Nothing's changed, Dev.
You still get angry at everything.

1542
03:04:39.667 --> 03:04:41.542 line:82%
Anger's my own. Doesn't leave me.

1543
03:04:44.657 --> 03:04:46.167 line:82%
Love can always leave and go.

1544
03:04:47.375 --> 03:04:50.037 line:82%
What will you do if you find
your lost love?

1545
03:04:51.417 --> 03:04:55.917 line:82%
What will I say now, Maya.
I'll just say 'go back'.

1546
03:04:56.917 --> 03:04:57.750 line:82%
Just go.

1547
03:04:58.500 --> 03:04:59.417 line:82%
Dev...

1548
03:05:02.000 --> 03:05:06.167 line:82%
Only I know how I have
survived these three years.

1549
03:05:08.417 --> 03:05:12.417 line:82%
There was not a moment in the day
when I didn't think of you.

1550
03:05:14.042 --> 03:05:19.125 line:82%
But I used to convince myself
that you are alright.

1551
03:05:20.792 --> 03:05:24.292 line:82%
That you are happy with your family.

1552
03:05:25.625 --> 03:05:27.458 line:82%
I used to think of your happiness

1553
03:05:29.017 --> 03:05:30.958 line:82%
and it would reduce a bit
of my unhappiness.

1554
03:05:34.167 --> 03:05:35.792 line:82%
But today I realized

1555
03:05:36.667 --> 03:05:40.797 line:82%
that you have been as alone as I am.

1556
03:05:45.458 --> 03:05:46.292 line:82%
Yes, Dev.

1557
03:05:48.333 --> 03:05:53.083 line:82%
Even I have been alone for three years.

1558
03:05:54.083 --> 03:05:55.997 line:82%
Alone, just like you.

1559
03:06:01.083 --> 03:06:02.125 line:82%
Why, Dev?

1560
03:06:03.583 --> 03:06:06.477 line:82%
Why did all this happen? Why?

1561
03:06:06.917 --> 03:06:09.708 line:82%
Why did we meet? And then part?

1562
03:06:10.667 --> 03:06:13.208 line:82%
Why, Dev? Why?

1563
03:06:27.333 --> 03:06:29.333 line:82%
Everyone shares happiness and sorrow.

1564
03:06:30.837 --> 03:06:33.042 line:82%
I want to share my punishment with you.

1565
03:06:34.625 --> 03:06:37.917 line:82%
My life may not be complete
